            "title": "劍橋科技AH股同步創新高！H股盤中狂飆37%，A股直線升停",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周五，4月17日，劍橋科技 (HK:6166) (SS:603083)AH股同步創新高，H股盤中狂飆37%最高觸及125.9港元，A股升停報145.29元人民幣。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"582\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eebjE3WMt2lBzp8jzIKqlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/d2c263522af8622859f29d125dcd62cd\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q0o38yao4FPnE4OPEmDCZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/ec3eb8b9f0ea52a8842470e10e3a42e0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，光模組龍頭業績超預期引爆板塊情緒。中際旭創發佈2026年第一季度財報——營收194.96億元，同比增長192.12%；歸母淨利潤57.35億元，同比增長262.28%，均大幅超出市場預期。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-df9e28c6-5fa9-3047-93db-c9b58fcb3e85-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球光通信器件龍頭Lumentum近期表示，數據中心需求高景氣下，現有產能已供不應求，預計兩個季度後2028年產能將全部售罄。中國銀河證券據此指出，AI驅動光模組加速反覆運算，800G/1.6T光模組迎來快速放量，高速光模組帶動測試儀器需求增長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 