        {
            "title": "需求現形｜Cybertruck需求現形 去年第4季近兩成銷售靠SpaceX等「自已人」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SFfwijRexLRNMClcLqdWIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/bd8352c4c2e3be8ea396133e30b5bd93\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特斯拉（Tesla）Cybertruck的銷售數據再次引發市場關注。S&amp;P Global Mobility數據顯示，Cybertruck的銷售情況遠不如表面亮眼，其中近兩成訂單來自同屬<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"馬斯克\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:馬斯克;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬斯克\">馬斯克</a>旗下的SpaceX等，而若扣除這些「自已人」訂單，Cybertruck在美國的年增率將出現高達51%的衰退，而非官方數據所呈現的情況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博引述相關數據報道，美國去年第4季共登記7,071輛Cybertruck，其中竟有1,279輛由SpaceX購買、佔比高達18%；若再加上xAI、The Boring Company與Neuralink等關聯企業，總計達1,339輛，接近整體銷量的20%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d7c9ca95-a43e-30e7-8438-87878dba8eaa-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以當時單價計算，特斯拉透過向馬斯克旗下的企業銷售車輛，等於為自身賬面創造了超過1億美元的收入。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事實上，早在去年10月，就有大量Cybertruck被拍到運往SpaceX基地與xAI據點，該公司工程師也曾證實，這些企業正在以Cybertruck替換原有車隊。最新數據則進一步證實，至今年1月與2月，馬斯克旗下企業仍持續購入Cybertruck。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一情況引發了對特斯拉實際市場表現的擔憂。因為若剔除這些內部交易，Cybertruck的真實銷售速度遠低於預期。當初馬斯克對外宣稱年銷量可達25萬輛，但目前實際僅約2萬輛，不到目標的1成。業界分析更直言，市場對這款車的需求正在快速枯竭。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%8F%BE%E5%BD%A2-cybertruck%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%8F%BE%E5%BD%A2-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%AC%AC4%E5%AD%A3%E8%BF%91%E5%85%A9%E6%88%90%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%9D%A0spacex%E7%AD%89-%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B2%E4%BA%BA-034309402.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 11:52:20",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜Netflix第二季業績預測遜預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜Netflix第二季業績預測遜預期\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Netflix\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Netflix;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Netflix\">Netflix</a>第二季業績預測遜預期</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博報道，Netflix預測當前的第二1季度每股純利為78美分，低於市場預期的84美分，拖累公司收市後時段下跌超過9%。此外亦公布，聯合創始人Reed Hastings將繼在董事會任職29年後卸任，以追求慈善事業和個人興趣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Netflix今年前三個月收入增長16%至123億美元，高過市場預期的122億美元；每股純利為1.23美元，亦高過市場預期的0.76美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華爾街如今正在觀察Netflix能否留住訂閱用戶。Netflix在3月上調了訂閱價格，將無廣告的標準套餐價格提高了2美元，至每月20美元。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-netflix%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%A3%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E9%81%9C%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-033430084.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 11:38:08",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜據美國高官與油企代表舉行視像會議促增本土產油量",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜據美國高官與油企代表舉行視像會議促增本土產油量\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜據美國高官與油企代表舉行視像會議促增本土產油量</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《彭博》報道，美國內政部長Doug Burgum及能源部長Chris Wright與美國主要油企高層舉行視像會議，敦促增加本土產油量。報道指，與會油企包括埃克森美孚(美：XOM)、雪佛龍(美：CVX)、Continental Resources(美：CLR)、Diamondback Energy(美：FANG)、Devon Energy(美：DVN)及西方石油(美：OXY)等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道指，政府方面強調，鑑於強勁價格信號及穩定市場必要性，短期內有進一步增產機會，亦重申不打算對原油出口實施限制。油企方面反應謹慎。基於中東石油供應中斷持續多久仍存不確定性，很多生產商不願大幅擴產。期貨市場持續顯示未來數月油價回落，進一步強化業界在資本支出的謹慎取態。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9c944fbd-e7e9-37c1-9504-a970eee163dc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油企反指結構性限制可能阻礙短期產量增長，包括可能延長項目的許可審批延誤，以及影響營運靈活性的監管限制。部分人士亦建議放寬對天然氣燃燒的限制，讓缺乏足夠天然氣外輸能力油井產出更多原油。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E6%93%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E8%88%87%E6%B2%B9%E4%BC%81%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E8%A6%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E4%BF%83%E5%A2%9E%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E7%94%A2%E6%B2%B9%E9%87%8F-030008764.html",
